This is a phase III, multicenter, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled study planning to include approximately 387 T2DM patients who have received at least 8 weeks of treatment with diet control and exercise; have not received any glucose-lowering agents within the 8 weeks prior to screening; and have inadequately controlled blood glucose.

The subjects would receive PEX168 or placebo monotherapy for 52weeks in total.

